    General Stores in Juhu, Mumbai

    In India, general stores or mom-n-pop shops are generally referred to as 'kiranas'. It is a form of traditional retail where it offers a wide range of products. In certain metros and cities, a general store can also be a part of a pharmacy or medicine shop. These retail stores are a part of the sales network of most FMCG brands and leading manufacturing companies. A modern general store may have air-conditioning, a wider range of products and services that local shops may not offer. Catering to the convenience of their customers, these shops also extend free home delivery service. Aiming for the convenience of the locals, these general stores also offer complimentary doorstep delivery services. You can find one from a large number of General Stores in Juhu, Mumbai from the list given above.
